data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bath home has been recently remodeled and comes with many extras. Newly remodeled kitchen features include hardwood soft close cabinets, granite countertops, recessed LED dimmable lighting, stainless steel appliances, and waterproof LVP throughout kitchen, living room, hallways and guest bath. New carpet, light fixtures/ceiling fans throughout, Upgraded smooth ceilings, New paint and drywall. The master bedroom has a walk in closet. Master Bathroom is a total remodel which comes complete with new  recessed dimmable LED lighting,  walk in tile shower, 21'Jacuzzi soaking tub with a mounted TV! Recently installed new French Doors that lead outside to the . backyard  which has new fencing, deck railing. and a large shed for storage. Front porch has newly installed posts. This home is a must see.!
